text: Mandeep Kaur (born 8 September 1988) is a Delhiite cricketer.Players She initially played for Assam and East zone, Since 2012 she has played for Delhi and North zone. She has played four First-class, fifty List A and thirty-one Twenty20 matches. == References == Category:1988 births Category:Assam women cricketers Category:Delhi women cricketers Category:East Zone women cricketers Category:North Zone women cricketers Category:Living people
